Quote:  A former Gore stablehand was arrested and held in jail being caught red-handed milkshaking a horse in the United States... Milkshaking is the illegal practice of tubing a mixture into a horse's stomach to delay the onset of lactic acid buildup in the muscles and enhance stamina.
